tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE coach_feedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  coach_name VARCHAR(50),
  athlete_name VARCHAR(50),
  feedback_text TEXT,
  strategy VARCHAR(100),
  game_plan TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE performance_strategies (
  strategy_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  strategy_name VARCHAR(255),
  strategy_description TEXT,
  coach_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (coach_id) REFERENCES coach_feedback(feedback_id)
);

CREATE TABLE CoachFeedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    coach_id INT,
    player_id INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    feedback_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE Strategies (
    strategy_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    player_id INT,
    strategy_name VARCHAR(50),
    strategy_description TEXT,
    strategy_category VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE GamePlans (
    game_plan_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    player_id INT,
    game_plan_name VARCHAR(50),
    game_plan_description TEXT,
    game_plan_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE Players (
    player_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    player_name VARCHAR(50),
    player_position VARCHAR(50),
    player_team VARCHAR(50),
    player_age INT
);

CREATE TABLE Coaches (
    coach_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    coach_name VARCHAR(50),
    coach_team VARCHAR(50),
    coach_experience_years INT,
    coach_specialty VARCHAR(50)
);
